channel.title: Post here the songs that mean everything to you
channel.description:
This is probably already a thing but screw it. If you have any song that means the world to you in someway post it here (and describe that connection if you want).
The song that means the most to me is Combine by Bustre. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ig44rDYo8IM
This song was released during a time in my life where I was depressed and really sad. Combine struck a chord with me and has always been one of my favorite songs for me. I could relate to it back then because it was his last DnB song on his Bustre alias and was really melancholic amidst all the happy sounding synths. It served as a way to show that even though you may sound happy saying goodbye, you can always be sad about it and you are always allowed to show your emotions. It doesn't have to end the bad way. There will always be a better choice. There is always an answer...
